ha%2C%20Madhu%20Chandak%2C%20Puneet%20Dalmia%2C%20Siddharth%20Yog%2C%20Deep%20Kalra%20and%20Ziaa%20Lalkaka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDas%20initially%20agreed%20to%20cooperate%20with%20committee%20proceedings%2C%20but%20later%20put%20in%20his%20papers.%20Senior%20faculty%20from%20the%20economics%20department%20tried%20to%20get%20Das%20to%20withdraw%20his%20resignation%20but%20the%20latter%20was%20adamant%20that%20he%20would%20not%20do%20so%20unless%20alleged%20restrictions%20placed%20on%20him%20when%20it%20came%20to%20speaking%20about%20this%20paper%20were%20lifted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFaculty%20at%20the%20meeting%20had%20unanimously%20agreed%20that%20Das%20must%20be%20reinstated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBalakrishnan%E2%80%99s%20letter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPulapre%20Balakrishnan%20had%20quit%20the%20university%20close%20on%20Das%E2%80%99s%20heels.%20As%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fsecond-professor-quits-as-democratic-backsliding-row-continues-to-roil-ashoka-university%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20Das%20was%20an%20assistant%20professor%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ashoka.edu.in%2Fprofile%2Fpulapre-balakrishnan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBalakrishnan%20is%20a%20full%20professor%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0who%20joined%20the%20private%20university%20in%202015%20after%20working%20at%20Oxford%20University%2C%20the%20Indian%20Statistical%20Institute%2C%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%20in%20Kozhikode%20and%20the%20World%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20August%2019%20letter%20to%20Chancellor%20Mukherjee%20and%20founder%20and%20trustee%20Pramath%20Raj%20Sinha%2C%20Balakrishnan%20has%20urged%20the%20governing%20body%20to%20consider%20inviting%20Das%20to%20return%20to%20the%20post%2C%20if%20they%20have%20not%20already.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20for%20myself%2C%20I%20am%20moving%20on.%20I%20have%20resigned%20my%20position%20based%20on%20my%20belief%20that%20there%20was%20a%20grave%20error%20of%20judgment%20in%20the%20response%20to%20the%20attention%20received%20by%20Das%E2%80%99s%20paper%20on%20social%20media.%20Academic%20freedom%20was%20violated%20in%20the%20response%2C%20and%20it%20would%20be%20unconscionable%20for%20me%20to%20remain%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20freedom%20to%20write%20critically%20about%20economic%20policy%20had%20been%20one%20of%20his%20stated%20clauses%20while%20joining.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20may%20recall%20our%20first%20meeting%20at%20the%20IIC%E2%80%99s%20coffee%20lounge%20in%202014.%20As%20for%20myself%2C%20I%20recall%20having%20asked%20you%20two%20questions.%20I%20had%20stated%20that%20I%20had%20for%20at%20least%20two%20decades%20by%20then%20been%20writing%20critically%20about%20economic%20policy%20in%20India%20and%20intend%20to%20continue%20to%20do%20so%20were%20I%20to%20join%20Ashoka%E2%80%99s%20faculty.%20Rudrangshu%20had%20responded%20by%20saying%20that%20the%20University%20did%20not%20expect%20its%20faculty%20to%20take%20any%20particular%20view%20on%20the%20matter%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNext%20I%20had%20declared%20that%20I%20was%20associated%20with%20the%20public%20campaign%20to%20repeal%20Section%20377%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(some%20tact%20was%20needed%20there%2C%20I%20guess).%20Pramath%20had%20responded%20by%20saying%20that%2C%20while%20the%20University%20appreciated%20the%20disclosure%2C%20it%20made%20no%20difference%20to%20it.%20I%20wish%20to%20place%20on%20record%20that%20in%20these%20eight%20years%20I%20have%20been%20here%2C%20the%20University%20has%20been%20true%20to%20its%20word.%20I%20have%20written%20extensively%20in%20the%20media%2C%20marched%20on%20the%20streets%20for%20my%20rights%20and%20expressed%20my%20thoughts%20in%20class%20without%20the%20slightest%20restraint%20placed%20in%20my%20path%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalakrishnan%20noted%20that%20the%20university%20also%20bank-rolled%20the%20publication%20of%20his%20book%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20Economy%20from%20Nehru%20to%20Modi%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20in%20its%20Hedgehog%20and%20Fox%20series.%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20have%20to%20meet%20anyone%20or%20even%20submit%20a%20proposal%20for%20this.%20The%20publisher%20informs%20me%20that%20the%20project%20was%20approved%20the%20moment%20that%20it%20was%20proposed.%20The%20study%20is%20the%20culmination%20of%20my%20professional%20work%20thus%20far%2C%20and%20is%20a%20no-holds-barred%20look%20at%20the%20economic%20history%20of%20our%20country%2C%20including%2C%20needless%20to%20mention%2C%20the%20present.%20For%20these%20opportunities%20afforded%20to%20me%2C%20I%20express%20my%20deepest%20gratitude%20to%20the%20foundation%20that%20you%20represent%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20parts%20of%20the%20letter%20act%20as%20a%20warning%20of%20times%20to%20come%20and%20what%20Ashoka%20University%20seeks%20to%20lose%20when%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20uphold%20academic%20freedom%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFinally%2C%20I%20am%20aware%20of%20the%20challenges%20you%20face%20in%20taking%20forward%20the%20mighty%20adventure%20that%20is%20Ashoka%20University.%20I%20was%20among%20the%20first%20faculty%20representatives%20of%20the%20IIM%20Kozhikode%2C%20have%20headed%20an%20autonomous%20economics%20research%20institute%20in%20the%20public%20sector%20and%20now%20run%20a%20modest%20private%20educational%20trust.%20In%20all%20these%20situations%20I%20have%20seen%20how%20terrifying%20it%20can%20be%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20government.%20Last%20night%20I%20was%20on%20national%20television%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20academic%20freedom%20in%20this%20country%2C%20where%20I%20spoke%20of%20the%20pressures%20from%20government%20that%20independent%20initiatives%20in%20higher%20education%20in%20this%20country%20face.%20As%20I%20continue%20to%20speak%20in%20future%2C%20some%20attention%20may%20inadvertently%20be%20drawn%20to%20Ashoka.%20However%2C%20anyone%20reading%20this%20document%2C%20which%20I%20intend%20to%20make%20public%20at%20some%20stage%2C%20cannot%20but%20recognise%20the%20brave%20and%20selfless%20attempt%20to%20provide%20India%20with%20a%20thriving%20space%20for%20intellectual%20activity%20that%20it%20represents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20economics%20department%20of%20the%20university%20said%20considering%20the%20welfare%20of%20students%2C%20teaching%20will%20not%20be%20disrupted%20due%20to%20their%20protest.%20%E2%80%9COur%20demands%20in%20the%20open%20letter%20stand.%20The%20welfare%20of%20students%20is%20of%20utmost%20priority%20to%20the%20Economics%20department.%20Therefore%2C%20teaching%20at%20no%20point%20will%20be%20disrupted.%20While%20we%20carry%20on%20with%20our%20academic%20responsibilities%2C%20we%20reserve%20the%20right%20to%20protest%20in%20other%20ways%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20department%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEconAtAshoka%2Fstatus%2F1692835256272068841%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20tweet%20posted%20on%20Saturday%2C%20August%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20thanked%20all%20departments%20of%20the%20university%20who%20issued%20statements%20in%20solidarity%20with%20the%20demands%20in%20their%20open%20letter.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20had%20meetings%20with%20the%20GB%20members%20and%20the%20VC%20and%20have%20been%20assured%20that%20a%20resolution%20is%20underway.%20We%20hope%20that%20our%20combined%20efforts%20yield%20favourable%20outcomes%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20economics%20department%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692444026000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16201010%2FAshoka.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fashoka-university-sabyasachi-das-pulapre-balakrishnan%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Senior%20economics%20professor%20Pula