e%20most%20across%20the%20state%20during%202008-12%20and%202014-21.%20In%20the%20first%20phase%2C%20I%20was%20working%20on%20my%20thesis%2C%20and%20in%20the%20second%20phase%2C%20I%20was%20working%20on%20my%20second%20monograph.%20During%20these%20times%2C%20I%20witnessed%20ideological%20battles%20in%20Jungle%20Mahal%20resulting%20in%20bloodshed%2C%20bombs%20being%20thrown%2C%20dead%20bodies%2C%20middlemen%20in%20the%20farming%20sector%20turning%20violent%2C%20rising%20corruption%2C%20and%20religious%20polarisation.%C2%A0And%2C%20the%20political%20leaders%20who%20either%20killed%20their%20rivals%20or%20themselves%20got%20murdered%20in%20the%20political%20violence%20were%20from%20across%20castes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20301px)%2085vw%2C%20301px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19153416%2F61ZvUODO0WL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22301%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19153416%2F61ZvUODO0WL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%20656w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19153416%2F61ZvUODO0WL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-197x300.jpg%20197w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668711%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22458%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Curious%20Trajectory%20of%20Caste%20in%20West%20Bengal%20Politics%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20Ayan%20Guha.%20Publisher%3A%20Brill%20Academic%20Publishers.%20Photo%3A%20amazon.in.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELately%2C%20Bengal%20violence%20is%20more%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ijcv.org%2Findex.php%2Fijcv%2Farticle%2Fview%2F3119%5C%22%3Ecommunal%20sentiment%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20not%20about%20caste.%20As%20I%20was%20reading%20scholars%2C%20no%20one%20really%20talked%20much%20about%20caste%20as%20a%20category%20of%20political%20relevance%20in%20West%20Bengal%20except%20for%20Praskanva%20Sinharay.%20In%20his%20writings%20for%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20and%20Political%20Weekly%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3ESinharay%20attempted%20to%20put%20forward%20an%20argument%20that%20the%20historically%20ignored%20category%20of%20caste%20in%20the%20state%20is%20making%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epw.in%2Fjournal%2F2016%2F9%2Fcommentary%2Fdalit-question-upcoming-west-bengal-assembly-elections.html%5C%22%3Eunprecedented%20upsurge%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20carrying%20the%20potential%20to%20influence%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20the%20examples%20of%20Matuas%E2%80%99%20assertion%20and%20the%20responses%20of%20political%20parties%20%E2%80%93%20most%20conspicuously%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20and%20the%20rising%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20%E2%80%93%20Sinharay%20argued%20that%20there%20is%20not%20only%20a%20rise%20of%20caste%20politics%20but%20also%20a%20rise%20of%20Dalit%20assertion.%20However%2C%20without%20problematising%20such%20terms%20as%20caste%20politics%2C%20and%20Dalit%20assertion%20and%20its%20implications%20to%20the%20existing%20context%2C%20claiming%20a%20role%20of%20caste%20in%20Bengal%20politics%20seemed%20a%20premature%20assumption%20and%20methodologically%20problematic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaste%20in%20Bengal%20politics%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202021%20assembly%20election%20results%20didn%E2%80%99t%20really%20show%20caste%20as%20an%20emerging%20category.%20Matua%20issue%2C%20however%2C%20remained%20important%20and%20intriguing%2C%20but%20quite%20localised.%20To%20my%20surprise%2C%20Ayan%20Guha%20came%20out%20with%20a%20book-length%20endeavour%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20caste%20issue%20to%20effectively%20dismantle%20the%20carefully%20orchestrated%20conceptualisation%20of%20caste%20as%20a%20political%20category%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20Before%20I%20go%20into%20Guha%E2%80%99s%20latest%20book%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Curious%20Trajectory%20of%20Caste%20in%20West%20Bengal%20Politics%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3EI%20would%20like%20to%20pose%20some%20of%20the%20key%20general%20questions%20that%20one%20needs%20to%20ask%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20caste%20issue%20in%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwest-bengal-election-matuas-namashudras-bjp-identity-politics-orakandi-citizenship-caa%5C%22%3EBengal%E2%80%99s%20Matuas%20Are%20Caught%20Between%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Identity%20Politics%20and%20the%20Citizenship%20Concern%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20what%20does%20it%20mean%20to%20be%20an%20upper%20caste%20or%20lower%20caste%20in%20West%20Bengal%20if%20one%20compares%20it%20with%20any%20other%20state%20where%20caste%20is%20perceived%20to%20be%20an%20important%20category%3F%20Second%2C%20what%20does%20it%20mean%20to%20be%20oppressed%20because%20of%20being%20lower%20caste%20in%20West%20Bengal%3F%20And%20finally%2C%20how%20far%20and%20in%20what%20ways%20dominant%20political%20discourse%20revolves%20around%20the%20issues%20of%20caste%20in%20West%20Bengal%3F%20Can%20one%20attempt%20to%20use%20the%20same%20formula%20of%20caste%20in%20Bengal%20politics%20like%20one%20can%20in%20places%20like%20Karnataka%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20not.%20Instead%20of%20trying%20to%20find%20out%20where%20is%20caste%20in%20politics%2C%20the%20important%20question%20should%20therefore%20be%2C%20why%20caste%20is%20not%20found%20in%20politics%20in%20West%20Bengal%3F%20For%20that%2C%20we%20have%20a%20range%20of%20answers.%20For%20example%2C%20Dwaipayan%20Bhattacharyya%20explains%20it%20with%20the%20help%20of%20his%20theoretical%20formulation%20of%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epw.in%2Fjournal%2F2009%2F09%2Flocal-government-rural-west-bengal-special-issues-specials%2Fcontrol-and-factions%5C%22%3Eparty%20society%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99.%20The%20author%20of%20this%20article%2C%20Suman%20Nath%2C%20used%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epw.in%2Fjournal%2F2018%2F28%2Fspecial-articles%2F%25E2%2580%2598cultural-misrecognition%25E2%2580%2599-and-sustenance.html%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98systemic%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epw.in%2Fjournal%2F2022%2F40%2Fspecial-articles%2Fpolitics-cultural-misrecognitions-and-rise.html%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98cultural%20misrecognition%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20of%20overarching%20party%20and%20then%20the%20rise%20of%20religious%20identity%20in%20Bengal%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20by%20Guha%20does%20not%20give%20a%20straightforward%20answer%20to%20these%20pressing%20questions%2C%20rather%20it%20gracefully%20deals%20with%20the%20nuances%20of%20the%20caste%20puzzle%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20Guha%20addresses%20caste%20in%20West%20Bengal%20in%20a%20way%20that%20can%20be%20seen%20as%20studying%20an%20absent-present%20category.%20He%20rightly%20argues%20that%20caste%20is%20present%20as%20a%20social%20category%20and%2C%20surprisingly%2C%20absent%20as%20a%20political%20category%20and%20this%20is%20precisely%20where%20the%20whole%20idea%20of%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20exceptionalism%20arises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20certain%20accounts%20%E2%80%93%20including%20the%20writings%20of%20Manoranjan%20Byapari%20%E2%80%93%20Guha%20shows%20that%20caste-based%20oppression%20is%20not%20uncommon%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20Referring%20to%20the%20theoretical%20explanations%20of%20%E2%80%98structuring%20structure%E2%80%99%20by%20Bourdieu%2C%20Guha%20poses%20his%20central%20problem%20as%20the%20curious%20absence%20of%20caste.%20Since%20caste%20has%20been%20a%20constant%20social%20factor%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Guha%20argues%2C%20it%20might%20have%20shaped%20certain%20political%20aspects%20that%20might%20have%20been%20overlooked%20by%20scholars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20one%20reads%20the%20book%2C%20it%20gives%20more%20concrete%20evidence%20that%20goes%20against%20the%20caste%20mobilisation%20thesis.%20The%20chapter%20on%20political%20representation%20shows%20that%20there%20is%20hardly%20any%20mobilisation%20of%20lower%20caste%20groups%20since%202011%20when%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20defeated%20the%2034-year-long%20Left%20Front%20rule.%20In%20fact%2C%20a%20comparative%20analysis%20of%20the%20demographic%20nature%20of%20Left%20Front%20and%20TMC%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20really%20show%20much%20of%20a%20difference.%20Guha%20emphatically%20argues%2C%20on%20page%2095%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20%E2%80%98rise%20of%20caste%20thesis%E2%80%99%20while%20making%20a%20sweeping%20generalisation%20has%20not%20bothered%20to%20make%20a%20comparison%20between%20the%20trends%20of%20lower%20caste%20political%20representation%20during%20the%20Left%20rule%20and%20the%20same%20during%20the%20post-%20Left%20era.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F18142117%2FF069qJ9aIAAFhde.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F18142117%2FF069qJ9aIAAFhde.jpeg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F18142117%2FF069qJ9aIAAFhde-300x212.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F18142117%2FF069qJ9aIAAFhde-1024x723.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663769%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22763%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentational%20image.%20Left%20parties%20protest%20alleged%20election%20rigging%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40SitaramYechury%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20this%20clears%20his%20stand%20for%20the%20entire%20work%2C%20he%20meticulously%20discusses%20the%20question%20of%20%E2%80%98absent-present%E2%80%99%20by%20looking%20at%20the%20demographic%2C%20economic%2C%20and%20political%20culture.%20In%20each%20of%20the%20sections%2C%20the%20book%20provides%20a%20structural%20explanation%20of%20two%20things%3A%20first%2C%20what%20is%20it%20that%20is%20an%20exception%20in%20Bengal%2C%20and%20second%2C%20why%20it%20is%20an%20exception.%20For%20those%20questions%2C%20he%20cites%20examples%20of%20the%20demographic%20veracity%20of%20the%20castes%20and%20diverse%20arrays%20of%20interests%20which%20are%20difficult%20to%20culminate%20into%20any%20singular%20demand%20forming%20what%20has%20happened%20as%20%E2%80%98Mandalisation%E2%80%99%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20while%20rural%20belts%20do%20have%20a%20few%20land-holding%20castes%2C%20this%20is%20quite%20unique%20in%20West%20Bengal%20that%20lower%20caste%20groups%20are%20not%20necessarily%20poor%20or%20landless%20%E2%80%93%20a%20fact%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.co.in%2Fbooks%2Fabout%2FRural_Commercial_Capital.html%3Fid%3DRfMTAQAAIAAJ%26redir_esc%3Dy%5C%22%3EHarriss-White%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F329701431_Political_economy_of_cold_storages_in_West_Bengalpdf%5C%22%3ENath%20and%20Chakrabarti%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epw.in%2Fjournal%2F2021%2F15%2Fspecial-articles%2Ffarmers%25E2%2580%2599-politics-west-bengal.html%5C%22%3ENath%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20cited%20through%20their%20ethnographic%20works%20over%20the%20years.%20In%20dealing%20with%20the%20domains%20of%20political%20culture%2C%20the%20book%20shows%20in%20what%20ways%20the%20%3Cem%3EBhadralok%20culture%3C%2Fem%3E%20template%20is%20still%20pervasive%20enough%20to%20withstand%20caste%20identity%20mobilisation%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20book%20addresses%20structural%20issues%20based%20on%20secondary%20sources%20with%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20compilation%20works%2C%20Guha%E2%80%99s%20snapshot%20ethnography%20on%20caste%20in%20everyday%20life%20opens%20up%20new%20potential%20for%20future%20works.%20Here%2C%20the%20book%20talks%20about%20the%20relative%20autonomy%20of%20the%20village%20leaders%20under%20TMC%20where%20the%20party%20diktat%20on%20everyday%20village%20matters%20is%20less%20if%20one%20compares%20it%20to%20the%20Left%20Front.%20This%20in%20part%2C%20according%20to%20Guha%2C%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20caste%20identity%20assertion.%20While%2C%20theoretically%2C%20this%20goes%20well%20with%20the%20existing%20literature%20on%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20regime%20of%20politics%20of%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epw.in%2Fjournal%2F2022%2F40%2Fspecial-articles%2Fpolitics-cultural-misrecognitions-and-rise.html%5C%22%3Emisrecognition%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20alongside%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cambridge.org%2Fcore%2Fbooks%2Fgovernment-as-practice%2FDC253A808690F68F04FE5DB2F52AC8BE%5C%22%3Eparty%20society%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20work%20being%20a%20snapshot%20ethnography%20is%20limited%20in%20its%20scope%20of%20mapping%20the%20village%20narrative%20to%20the%20wider%20caste%20assertion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20most%20original%20contribution%20towards%20the%20understanding%20of%20identity%20(and%20not%20caste)%20issue%20is%20to%20be%20located%20in%20the%20chapter%20on%20%E2%80%98politics%20of%20memory%E2%80%99.%20Here%2C%20Guha%20shows%20how%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20its%20Hindutva%20brigade%20have%20used%20Matuas%E2%80%99%20critical%20position%20related%20to%20the%20citizenship%20issue%20on%20the%20one%20hand%20and%20their%20insecurity%20and%20painful%20memories%20of%20partition-related%20exodus%20because%20of%20Islamic%20fundamentalism%20in%20Bangladesh%20on%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20this%20chapter%20onwards%2C%20most%20of%20the%20book%20revolves%20around%20finding%20out%20the%20structural%20reasons%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98absent-present%E2%80%99%20phenomenon%20of%20caste%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20As%20one%20arrives%20at%20the%20conclusions%2C%20the%20book%20recaps%20the%20fact%20that%20if%20there%20is%20indeed%20an%20identity%20assertion%20happening%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20it%20is%20happening%20along%20the%20line%20of%20religion.%20The%20BJP%20has%20successfully%20made%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20mobilisation%20of%20the%20Matuas%E2%80%A6%20from%20a%20caste%20conscious%20activity%20into%20a%20process%20of%20Hinduisation%20of%20Dalits%E2%80%9D%2C%20Guha%20concludes%20on%20page%20263.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Curious%20Trajectory%20of%20Caste%20in%20Bengal%20%3C%2Fem%3Etakes%20up%20an%20almost%20forgotten%20issue%20of%20caste%20in%20West%20Bengal%20and%20does%20meticulous%20work%20to%20show%3A%20a)%20Why%20it%20is%20structurally%20difficult%20for%20the%20caste%20issue%20to%20get%20prominence%20in%20the%20state%20and%20b)%20How%20an%20identity-based%20assertion%20was%20mistaken%20as%20the%20rise%20of%20caste.%20The%20book%20engages%20itself%20with%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20existing%20literature%20which%20also%20makes%20it%20quite%20%E2%80%98fat%E2%80%99%20considering%20the%20issue%20that%20it%20addresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Guha%20must%20be%20praised%20for%20writing%20a%20book-length%20piece%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20his%20excessive%20engagement%20with%20the%20existing%20literature%20on%20caste%20elsewhere%20is%20both%20intriguing%20and%20sometime%20distracting.%20Understandably%20this%20is%20linked%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20available%20materials%20on%20caste%20issues%20in%20West%20Bengal%20which%20pushed%20him%20to%20use%20examples%20of%20studies%20and%20theories%20developed%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20to%20this%20methodological%20problem%20is%20more%20ethnographic%20works%20and%20a%20scholar%20further%20looking%20into%20the%20caste%20issue%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20who%20can%20think%20of%20conducting%20intense%20ethnographic%20works%20to%20find%20out%20micro%20reasons%20for%20caste%20being%20present%20as%20a%20social%20category%20and%20absent%20as%20a%20political%20category.%20Guha%E2%80%99s%20work%20should%20be%20treated%20as%20a%20treasure%20to%20anyone%20looking%20for%20an%20understanding%20of%20existing%20scholarship%20on%20caste%20in%20India%20in%20general%20and%20a%20curious%20case%20of%20absent-present%20in%20West%20Bengal%20in%20particular.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESuman%20Nath%20teaches%20anthropology%20at%20Dr.%20APJ%20Abdul%20Kalam%20Government%20College%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20India.%20He%20has%20written%20extensively%20on%20Bengal%20politics%20in%20the%20recent%20past.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692441926000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F27105454%2Fflags.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fwhy-is-caste-an-absent-present-category-in-bengal-politics%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ayan%20Guha's%20latest%20book%2C%20'The%20Curious%20Trajectory%20of%20Caste%20in%20Bengal'%2C%20takes%20up%20an%20almost%20forgotten%20issue%20of%20caste%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20meticulously%20showing%20why%20it%20is%20structurally%20difficult%20for%20the%20issue%20to%20get%20prominence%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fwhy-is-caste-an-absent-present-category-in-bengal-politics%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Warren%20Buffett%2C%20Michael%20Burry%2C%20and%20other%20top%20investors%20revealed%20striking%20portfolio%20changes%20this%20week.%20Here%20are%204%20key%20trades.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221371%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22warren%20buffett%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F622627e6990863001998b2fb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22685%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWarren%20Buffett.%3Cp%3EKevin%20Lamarque%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWarren%20Buffett%2C%20Michael%20Burry%2C%20and%20others%20made%20striking%20changes%20to%20their%