3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20childhood%20my%20attitude%20was%20to%20never%20give%20up.%20I%20believe%20a%20lot%20in%20karma.%20Your%20job%20is%20to%20do%20your%20work%2C%20results%20depend%20on%20God.%20If%20you%20do%20that%20you%20won't%20have%20any%20regret.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20keep%20any%20regret%20in%20life.%20That%20was%20my%20motivation%20to%20keep%20working%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20right%20now%20working%20with%20sub-junior%20girls%20and%20I%20will%20try%20my%20best%20to%20give%20them%20what%20I%20have%20learnt%20in%20my%20early%20days.%20Side%20by%20side%20I%20will%20continue%20to%20work%20on%20my%20game%2C%20and%20whenever%20I%20get%20a%20chance%2C%20I%20will%20play%20again.%26quot%3B%20The%20poster%20girl%20of%20Indian%20women's%20hockey%20hopes%20to%20see%20the%20team%20on%20the%20podium%20at%20the%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStay%20positive%2C%20that%20is%20my%20mantra%2C%20I%20just%20try%20to%20stay%20positive%20always.%20I%20am%20trying%20hard%20and%20I%20proved%20myself%2C%20selection%20is%20not%20in%20my%20hands.%20I%20can%20only%20work%2C%20which%20I%20have%20been%20doing%20for%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20no%20regrets%20in%20life%2C%20I%20have%20achieved%20everything%20but%20an%20Olympic%20medal%20is%20something%20that%20is%20missing%20from%20my%20cupboard.%20I%20play%20or%20not%2C%20it%20doesn't%20matter%2C%20but%20I%20want%20the%20Indian%20women's%20hockey%20team%20on%20the%20Olympics%20podium%20one%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20preparing%20for%20Commonwealth%20Games%2C%20I%20was%20ready%20for%20Asian%20Games%20also%20but%20was%20not%20selected%2C%26quot%3B%20Rani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20India%20captain%20was%20bestowed%20with%20the%20Major%20Dhyan%20Chand%20Khel%20Ratna%20Award%20in%202020%20and%20also%20received%20the%20Padma%20Shri%2C%20the%20country's%20fourth%20highest%20civilian%20award%