ernment%20%E2%80%9Callowed%E2%80%9D%20the%20situation%20to%20flare%20up%20and%20has%20thereafter%20%E2%80%9Cturned%20a%20blind%20eye%E2%80%9D.%20This%20was%20reported%20by%20The%20Hindu%20on%20August%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20the%20Meitei%20Pangal%20community%2C%20which%20is%20only%208%25%20of%20the%20population%2C%20is%20hesitant%20and%20reluctant%20to%20criticise%20CM%20Biren%2C%20because%20he%E2%80%99s%20a%20Meitei%2C%20who%20are%2053%25%2C%20and%20adore%20him%2C%20Tampak%20clearly%20suggested%2C%20without%20explicitly%20saying%20so%2C%20that%20this%20was%20the%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20completely%20understandable%20that%20a%20small%20community%20of%20just%208%25%20would%20not%20want%20to%20in%20any%20way%20annoy%20the%2053%25%20majority%20of%20the%20state%2C%20which%20is%20why%20Tampak%20feels%20free%20to%20criticise%20the%20government%20in%20Delhi%20but%20is%20very%20uncomfortable%20and%20unwilling%20when%20similar%20questions%20are%20asked%20about%20the%20government%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20reason%2C%20if%20not%20also%20for%20others%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5fgj9k93FTs%26ab_channel%3DTheWire%5C%22%3Ethis%20is%20an%20interview%20you%20should%20see.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692440269000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19154251%2FKT-19-AUg.00_30_51_26.Still002.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwatch-muslim-meitei-pangal-karan-thapar-manipur%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22United%20Meitei-Pangal%20Committee%20spokesperson%20Mohammad%20Raees%20Ahmed%20Tampak%20is%20openly%20and%20unhesitatingly%20critical%20of%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20handling%20of%20the%20crisis%20in%20Manipur.%20He%20was%2C%20however%2C%20reluctant%20to%20criticise%20Chief%20Minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3