20London%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BHe's%20not%20happy%20about%20it%20at%20all.%20He's%20lost%20his%20job%20and%20his%20reputation%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20it%20was%20fair.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20devastated%20about%20it%2C%20because%20it's%20his%20life's%20work%2C%20basically.%20I've%20never%20known%20somebody%20who's%20so%20passionate%20about%20what%20he%20did.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20museum%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20several%20items%20of%20jewelry%20made%20of%20gold%2C%20semi-precious%20stones%2C%20and%20glass%2C%20dating%20from%20between%201%2C500%20BC%20and%20the%2019th%20century%20AD%2C%20were%20among%20those%20missing%2C%20The%20Telegraph%20reported.%20Other%20items%20had%20been%20damaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20piece%20of%20ancient%20Roman%20jewelry%20made%20from%20onyx%20%E2%80%93%20that%20a%20dealer%20said%20was%20valued%20between%20%C2%A325%2C000%20and%20%C2%A350%2C000%2C%20or%20%2432%2C000%20and%20%2463%2C000%20%E2%80%93%20was%20listed%20on%20eBay%20with%20a%20minimum%20price%20of%20%C2%A340%2C%20or%20around%20%2450%2C%20in%202016.%20Nobody%20made%20a%20bid%20for%20the%20treasure%2C%20however%2C%20The%20Telegraph%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20are%20now%20investigating%20the%20thefts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20museum%20has%20not%20properly%20cataloged%20all%20eight%20million%20items%20in%20its%20collection%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20easier%20for%20thefts%20to%20go%20undetected%2C%20sources%20told%20The%20Telegraph.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMajor%20things%20do%20get%20cataloged.%20There%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20minor%20things%20which%20are%20not%2C%20or%20which%20are%20all%20lumped%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Professor%20Martin%20Henig%2C%20a%20Roman%20art%20expert%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Oxford%2C%20told%20the%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20independent%20review%20is%20underway%20to%20establish%20what%20is%20missing%2C%20attempting%20to%20recover%20the%20missing%20items%20and%20preventing%20future%20thefts.%3