t%20of%20guidelines%20and%20preventive%20steps%20to%20be%20taken%20by%20states%20to%20prevent%20instances%20of%20mob%20lynching%20and%20hate%20speeches%20in%20the%20particular%202018%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20very%20clear.%20Whether%20it%20be%20one%20side%20or%20the%20other%20side%2C%20they%20have%20to%20be%20treated%20alike.%20If%20anyone%20indulges%20in%20anything%20which%20we%20know%20as%20%E2%80%98hate%20speech%E2%80%99%2C%20they%20will%20be%20dealt%20with%20as%20per%20the%20law.%20Something%20we%20have%20already%20expressed%20our%20opinion%20on.%20This%20does%20not%20need%20to%20be%20repeated%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Khanna%20said%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20bench%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-hate-speech-nuh-violence-boycott-calls-235536%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3ELivelaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20petitioners%20submitted%20to%20the%20court%20that%20during%20a%20rally%20held%20in%20Kerala%20by%20the%20young%20wing%20of%20the%20Indian%20Union%20of%20Muslim%20League%20(IUML)%20in%20July%2C%20a%20slogan%20was%20raised%20that%20said%20%E2%80%9Cdeath%20to%20the%20Hindus%E2%80%9D.%20To%20this%2C%20the%20court%20said%20hate%20speech%20by%20anyone%2C%20irrespective%20of%20their%20religion%2C%20will%20not%20be%20tolerated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20relation%20to%20the%20particular%20incident%20which%20the%20petitioner%20referred%20to%2C%20the%20Kerala%20Police%20booked%20over%20300%20people%2C%20including%20members%20from%20the%20youth%20wing%20of%20the%20IUML%2C%20for%20allegedly%20raising%20provocative%20slogans%20against%20Hindus.%20IUML%20is%20a%20constituent%20member%20of%20the%20Congress-led%20United%20Democratic%20Front%2C%20which%20is%20in%20opposition%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20hearing%20petitions%20on%20hate%20speech%20afresh%20on%20Friday%20after%20one%20Shaheen%20Abdullah%20moved%20the%20top%20court%20alleging%20instances%20of%20hate%20speeches%20made%20against%20Muslims%20during%20the%20recent%20Nuh%20violence%20in%20Haryana.%20The%20petitioner%20alleged%20that%20some%20of%20the%20Hindu%20groups%20issued%20open%20calls%20to%20boycott%20Muslims%2C%20telling%20shopkeepers%20not%20to%20employ%20Muslims%20in%20their%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20division%20bench%20allowed%20a%20week%E2%80%99s%20time%20to%20the%20Centre%20and%20Haryana%20government%20to%20come%20back%20with%20a%20response%20detailing%20whether%20or%20not%20instructions%20were%20given%20to%20authorities%20concerned%20regarding%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20committee%20to%20examine%20the%20material%20and%20verify%20if%20criminal%20cases%20were%20filed.%20As%20per%20the%202018%20judgment%2C%20the%20top%20court%20instructed%20state%20governments%20to%20form%20a%20committee%20and%20designate%20a%20nodal%20officer%20to%20register%20hate%20crimes%20and%20pursue%20investigations%20into%20such%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20its%202018%20judgment%2C%20the%20court%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20institute%20a%20mechanism%20with%20law%20enforcement%20officials%20at%20the%20local%20level%20to%20pursue%20matters%20of%20hate%20speech%20and%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20top%20court%20of%20the%20country%20does%20not%20become%20the%20first%20forum%20for%20an%20aggrieved%20party%20to%20approach%20for%20registration%20of%20FIRs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20its%202018%20verdict%20on%20hate%20speeches%2C%20the%20apex%20court%2C%20in%20October%202022%2C%20ordered%20police%20to%20immediately%20register%20cases%20against%20hate%20speech%20makers%20and%20offenders%20who%20committed%20acts%20of%20communal%20violence%20without%20waiting%20for%20a%20formal%20complaint%20to%20be%20filed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20listed%20the%20matter%20for%20the%20next%20hearing%20on%20August%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692436554000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2F14154412%2Fhate-speech.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ftreat-hate-speech-alike-independent-of-the-offenders-faith-sc-tells-police%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20court%20once%20again%20instructed%20states%20and%20Union%20territories%20to%20follow%20the%20guidelines%20it%20issued%20in%20the%20Tehseen%20Poonawala%20judgment%20(2018)%20to%20prevent%20instances%20of%20mob%20lynching%20and%20hate%20speeches.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ftreat-hate-speech-alike-independent-of-the-offenders-faith-sc-tells-police%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Auditor%20Report%20Revealed%20UDAN%20Scheme%20Didn't%20Work%20On%2093%25%20Routes%3A%20M%20Kharge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20on%20Saturday%20claimed%20that%20a%20CAG%20report%20has%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20Centre's%20flagship%20UDAN%20scheme%20did%20not%20work%20on%2093%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20routes%2C%20and%20said%20that%20the%20common%20people%20only%20got%20%26quot%3Blies%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bjumlas%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20regional%20connectivity%20scheme%20was%20launched%20under%20the%20name%20of%20UDAN%20(Ude%20Desh%20ka%20Aam%20Nagrik)%20on%20October%2021%2C%202016%2C%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20stimulate%20regional%20air%20connectivity%20and%20make%20air%20travel%20affordable%20to%20the%20masses%20in%20tier-2%20and%20tier-3%20cities%20and%20towns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20in%20Hindi%20on%20X%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%20that%20the%20PM%20Modi's%20government's%20promise%20of%20enabling%20those%20wearing%20slippers%20to%20travel%20by%20air%20has%20not%20been%20fulfilled%20%26quot%3Bjust%20like%20all%20their%20promises%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20saying%20this%2C%20the%20CAG%20Report%20is%20saying%20this!%20The%20scheme%20(UDAN)%20did%20not%20work%20on%2093%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20routes.%20Even%20independent%20audit%20of%20airlines%20was%20not%20done.%20The%20much%20publicised%20Helicopter%20services%20also%20remained%20stalled%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDidn't%20get%20'UDAN'%2C%20just%20talk%20of%20lies%20and%20jumlas!%20India%20will%20not%20forgive%20such%20an%20incompetent%20government%20now!%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20president%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20on%20Wednesday%20had%20also%20alleged%20the%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20(CAG)%20has%20pointed%20out%20%26quot%3Bscams%26quot%3B%20in%20infrastructure%20projects%20of%20the%20BJP-led%20central%20government%2C%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20should%20be%20held%20accountable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20should%20be%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20alleged%20scams%20and%20accountability%20should%20be%20fixed%2C%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Supriya%20Shrinate%20had%20said%2C%20asking%20when%20will%20the%20PM%20break%20his%20%26quot%3Bsilence%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20alleged%20irregularities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692436320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fin9f7gr8_mallikarjun-kharge-ani_625x300_27_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcag-report-on-udan-scheme-to-make-air-travel-affordable-says-it-didnt-work-on-93-routes-congress-president-4311088%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20on%20Saturday%20claimed%20that%20a%20CAG%20report%20has%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20Centre's%20flagship%20UDAN%20scheme%20did%20not%20work%20on%2093%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20routes%2C%20and%20said%20that%20the%20common%20people%20only%20got%20%26quot%3Blies%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bjumlas%26quo