Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20situation%20is%20such%20that%20anything%20can%20be%20distorted%20with%20a%20view%20to%20fashioning%20the%20next%20round%20of%20myths%20demonising%20Muslim%20citizens%20in%20India%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETake%20a%20recent%20news%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fncpcr-seeks-removal-of-controversial-book-from-darul-uloom-deobands-curriculum%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20the%20Protection%20of%20Child%20Rights%20(NCPCR)%20had%20taken%20up%20a%20complaint%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.manushi.in%2Fdarul-uloom-deoband-legitimizing-sexual-crimes-against-children%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EManushi%20Trust%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20regarding%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EDarul%20Uloom%20Deoband%E2%80%99s%20teachings%20to%20young%20students%20on%20ways%20to%20legitimise%20and%20normalise%20rape%2C%20sexual%20intercourse%20with%20minors%2C%20animals%2C%20dead%20bodies%2C%20impotent%20persons%20as%20well%20as%20anal%20sex%20with%20men%2C%20women%20and%20children%2C%20which%20may%20be%20against%20International%20Conventions%20and%2For%20the%20criminal%20laws%20of%20India.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20think%20that%20such%20allegations%20would%20be%20pooh-poohed%20because%20they%20concerned%20a%20prominent%2C%20world-class%20institution%20is%20to%20be%20na%C3%AFve%20in%20our%20times.%20Considering%20the%20propaganda%20that%20is%20unleashed%20against%20madrasas%20routinely%2C%20how%20difficult%20would%20it%20be%20to%20paint%20Muslims%20as%20mired%20in%20debauchery%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20any%20case%2C%20the%20propaganda%20succeeded%20in%20killing%20two%20birds%20with%20one%20stone%20%E2%80%93%20tarring%20the%20reputation%20of%20a%20prominent%20madrasa%20and%20projecting%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdiscreditable%20face%E2%80%9D%20of%20Muslim%20society.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20did%20not%20matter%20that%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.manushi.in%2Fdarul-uloom-deoband-legitimizing-sexual-crimes-against-children%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecomplaint%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20about%20a%20book%20titled%20%3Cem%3EBahishti%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Fbahishti-zewar_202005%2Fpage%2Fn7%2Fmode%2F2up%3Fview%3Dtheater%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Zewar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ebeing%20part%20of%20the%20curriculum%20was%20completely%20baseless.%20W%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eritten%20in%20the%20early%201900s%2C%20%3Cem%3EBahishti%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Zewar%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eis%20not%20part%20of%20the%20curriculum%20of%20any%20madrasa%20across%20the%20country%2C%20big%20or%20small%2C%20let%20alone%20the%20Darul%20Uloom%20Deoband.%20Nor%20any%20other%20publication%20of%20its%20kind.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20not%20part%20of%20any%20curriculum%2C%20%3Cem%3EBahishti%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Zewar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20often%20read%20by%20young%20women%20in%20their%20homes%2C%20especially%20after%20they%20got%20married.%20At%20one%20time%2C%20the%20book%20of%20instruction%20was%20an%20essential%20part%20of%20a%20bride%E2%80%99s%20trousseau.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%2C%20untouched%20by%20facts%2C%20spiced%20up%20reports%20about%20the%20reprehensible%20teachings%20being%20imparted%20at%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20prominent%20seminary%20appeared%20in%20many%20places%20and%2C%20by%20insinuation%2C%20became%20the%20horrific%20%E2%80%9Ctruth%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20as%20it%20were.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20same%20sequence%20of%20events%2C%20the%20RSS%20mouthpiece%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EOrganiser%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Forganiser.org%2F2023%2F07%2F23%2F182556%2Fbharat%2F182556%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Equoted%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3EMadhu%20Kishwar%2C%20founder%20and%20managing%20trustee%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.manushi.in%2Fdarul-uloom-deoband-legitimizing-sexual-crimes-against-children%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EManushi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20author%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Girl%20from%20Kathua%3A%20A%20Sacrificed%20Victim%20of%20Ghazwa-e-Hind%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eas%20saying%20that%20while%20a%20scrutiny%20of%20the%20entire%20curriculum%20of%20Darul%20Uloom%20was%20necessary%2C%20the%20seminary%20itself%20ought%20to%20be%20on%20the%20radar%20of%20intelligence%20agencies%20for%20playing%20with%20children%E2%80%99s%20minds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20complainant%20noted%20that%20the%20textbooks%20used%20in%20madrasas%20are%20invariably%20in%20Arabic%2C%20Urdu%20or%20Persian%20%E2%80%93%20the%20implication%20being%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cstrange%20material%E2%80%9D%20it%20had%20highlighted%20was%20just%20a%20small%20glimpse%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Csexual%20perversions%E2%80%9D%3B%20who%20knew%20what%20other%2C%20bigger%2C%20perversions%20were%20being%20legitimised%20through%20the%20teachings%20of%20madrasas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%20another%20point%20that%20was%20outlined%20in%20the%20complaint%20was%20that%20the%20author%20of%20%3Cem%3EBahishti%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Zewar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FAshraf_Ali_Thanwi%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAshraf%20Ali%20Thanawi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20had%20a%20following%20not%20only%20among%20Indian%20Muslims%20but%20also%20among%20members%20of%20organisations%20such%20as%20ISIS%2C%20Taliban%20and%20Al-Qaeda.%20Be%20it%20a%20question%20mark%20on%20the%20languages%20of%20instruction%20in%20madrasas%20or%20the%20mention%20of%20the%20above%20organisations%2C%20the%20intent%20of%20right-wing%20politics%20through%20this%20signalling%20is%20clear.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20necessary%20to%20remember%20that%20the%20complainant%2C%20right-wing%20activist%20Kishwar%2C%20remains%20an%20outspoken%20supporter%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi.%20Also%2C%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20a%20case%20was%20registered%20against%20her%20for%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F221966%2Fmadhu-kishwar-four-others-booked-for-allegedly-spreading-misinformation%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eallegedly%20spreading%20misinformation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20similar%20vein%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fright-wing-activist-madhu-kishwar-others-booked-for-allegedly-spreading-misinformation%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EKishwar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20in%20an%20offensive%20post%20had%20described%20Muslim%20men%20as%20%E2%80%9Ctrained%20stud%20bulls%E2%80%9D%20whose%20sexual%20prowess%20enables%20them%20to%20entice%20Hindu%2C%20Christian%20and%20Sikh%20women.%20She%20termed%20it%20%E2%80%9Csex%20jihad%E2%80%9D%20but%20took%20down%20the%20post%20later.%20She%20had%20also%20called%20the%20Pulitzer%20prize-winning%20Reuters%20photojournalist%2C%20late%20Danish%20Siddiqui%2C%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fright-wing-activist-madhu-kishwar-others-booked-for-allegedly-spreading-misinformation%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ejihadi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%20On%20July%2016%2C%202021%2C%20Siddiqui%2C%2038%2C%20was%20killed%20in%20Afghanistan%20while%20on%20assignment%2C%20in%20all%20probability%20by%20the%20Taliban%20or%20their%20supporters%20%E2%80%93%20the%20first%20journalist%20to%20lose%20his%20life%20while%20covering%20the%20Taliban%20offensive%20to%20seize%20control%20of%20Kabul.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20time%2C%20too%2C%20through%20the%20Trust%20a%20determined%20attempt%20was%20made%20to%20make%20Darul%20Uloom%20Deoband%20a%20target.%20However%2C%20the%20inquiry%20committee%20that%20was%20set%20up%20immediately%20to%20examine%20the%20allegations%20in%20the%20complaint%2C%20gave%20the%20institution%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bhaskar.com%2Flocal%2Futtar-pradesh%2Fsaharanpur%2Fdeoband%2Fnews%2Fthe-committee-probing-the-curriculum-gave-a-clean-chit-to-darul-uloom-131596551.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eclean%20chit%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20its%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdarululoom-deoband.com%2Fnews%2F%3Fp%3D453%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estatement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20Darul%20Uloom%20reiterated%20that%20from%20the%20go%20it%20had%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20book%20named%20in%20the%20complaint%20was%20not%20part%20of%20its%20curriculum.%20The%20institution%20termed%20the%20entire%20episode%20as%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdarululoom-deoband.com%2Fnews%2F%3Fp%3D453%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Econspiracy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20tarnish%20its%20reputation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHas%20the%20clean%20chit%20put%20an%20end%20to%20the%20controversy%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20entire%20sequence%20of%20events%20should%20also%20be%20seen%20as%20part%20of%20the%20ongoing%20campaign%20to%20demonise%20Muslim%20citizens.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20big%20question%20is%2C%20why%20did%20Kishwar%E2%80%99s%20Manushi%20Trust%20make%20a%20book%20that%20was%20not%20part%20of%20any%20madrasa%E2%80%99s%20curriculum%2C%20namely%20%3Cem%3EBahishti%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Fbahishti-zewar_202005%2Fpage%2Fn7%2Fmode%2F2up%3Fview%3Dtheater%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Zewar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20centrepiece%20of%20its%20complaint%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20straightforward%20explanation%20is%20that%20%3Cem%3EBahishti%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Zewar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20always%20been%20a%20contested%20text.%20Several%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Fislah-bahishti-zewar%2Fmode%2F2up%3Fview%3Dtheater%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebooks%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20have%20been%20written%20against%20it%2C%20fatwas%20given%20and%20many%20an%20article%20has%20stated%20that%20several%20parts%20of%20it%20should%20be%20done%20away%20with.%20That%20the%20mention%20of%20such%20a%20book%20would%20increase%20the%20believability%20quotient%20of%20the%20propaganda%20must%20have%20been%20a%20reason%20for%20its%20significant%20inclusion%20in%20the%20complaint.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20other%20big%20question%20is%2C%20does%20%3Cem%3EBahishti%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Zewar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20actually%20validate%20%E2%80%9Csexual%20perversions%E2%80%9D%3F%20Is%20it%20everything%20that%20the%20long-winded%20complaint%20paints%20it%20to%20be%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20truth%20is%20that%20the%20Trust%E2%80%99s%20complaint%20is%20a%20perfect%20example%20of%20how%20a%20text%20should%20not%20be%20read%20so%20as%20to%20assume%20dangerous%20overtones.%20Then%20it%20becomes%20a%20question%20of%20intent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20is%20%3Cem%3EBahishti%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EZewar%3C%2Fem%3E%20all%20about%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20stated%20earlier%20on%2C%20this%20book%2C%20written%20at%20the%20turn%20of%20the%2020%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century%20by%20Maulana%20Ashraf%20Ali%20Thanawi%2C%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20given%20to%20young%20women%20once%20they%20had%20read%20the%20Quran.%20It%20provides%20advice%20on%20the%20various%20aspects%20of%20life%20that%20shape%20the%20journey%20from%20birth%20to%20death%20%E2%80%93%20from%20aspects%20such%20as%20conduct%20in%20daily%20life%20to%20matters%20of%20faith.%20Instructions%20about%20the%20proper%20way%20to%20write%20letters%20sit%20alongside%20advice%20on%20hygiene%2C%20cures%20for%20illnesses%20and%20making%20household%20items.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20book%20also%20discusses%20aspects%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20life%20cycle%20such%20as%20menstruation%20and%20sexual%20intercourse%20%E2%80%93%20aspects%20that%20had%20been%20criticised%20from%20the%20very%20beginning%20for%20being%20too%20explicit.%20In%20fact%2C%20when%20iconic%20Urdu%20writer%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fismat-chughtai-birth-anniversary%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIsmat%20Chughtai%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20facing%20charges%20of%20obscenity%2C%20questions%20were%20raised%20about%20her%20religious%20upbringing%2C%20or%20lack%20of%20it.%20This%20is%20what%20she%20had%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Fkaghazi-hai-pairahan-ismat-chughtai%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esay%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20have%20read%20%3Cem%3EBahishti%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Zewar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20it%20is%20so%20open%20about%20everything%E2%80%A6When%20I%20read%20it%20in%20childhood%20it%20sounded%20jarring%2C%20dirty.%20When%20I%20read%20it%20after%20my%20BA%20I%20realised%20that%20the%20things%20discussed%20%5Bin%20it%5D%20were%20not%20dirty%3B%20rather%20they%20were%20relevant%20matters%20that%20every%20sensible%20person%20ought%20to%20know%20about.%20Although%2C%20if%20people%20have%20a%20mind%20to%20do%20it%2C%20they%20would%20label%20books%20taught%20in%20psychology%20and%20medical%20courses%20as%20obscene%2C%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWas%20Ismat%20Chughtai%E2%80%99s%20statement%20simply%20a%20defence%20tactic%20or%20is%20it%20true%20that%20texts%20like%20%3Cem%3EBahishti%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Zewar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20have%20to%20be%20read%20at%20an%20appropriate%20age%20when%20the%20individual%20has%20attained%20the%20maturity%20to%20understand%20it%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20if%20someone%20were%20to%20argue%20that%20Ismat%20Chughtai%E2%80%99s%20statement%20was%20simply%20a%20defence%20tactic%2C%20the%20larger%20and%20more%20important%20point%2C%20namely%20that%20texts%20like%20%3Cem%3EBahishti%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Zewar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20have%20to%20be%20read%20at%20an%20appropriate%20age%20when%20the%20individual%20has%20attained%20the%20maturity%20to%20understand%20it%2C%20hold%20true.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPerhaps%20that%20is%20why%20the%20well-known%20litterateur%2C%20prose%20stylist%20and%20journalist%2C%20Khwaja%20Hasan%20Nizami%20(1879-1955)%2C%20initially%20described%20%3Cem%3EBahishti%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Zewar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20the%20first%20obscene%20book%20in%20Urdu%20but%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rekhta.org%2Febooks%2Faawaz-e-dost-mukhtar-masood-ebooks-1%3Flang%3Dur%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewithdrew%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20his%20statement%20later.%20And%20that%20may%20be%20the%20reason%20why%20so%20many%20critics%20warn%20against%20even%20glancing%20at%20it%2C%20saying%20it%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eharam%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20or%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Fislah-bahishti-zewar%2Fmode%2F2up%3Fview%3Dtheater%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eforbidden%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20apart%20from%20those%20who%20may%20have%20valid%20objections%20against%20some%20sections%20of%20%3Cem%3EBahishti%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Zewar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20there%20are%20those%20whose%20deliberate%20act%20of%20mis-reading%20takes%20them%20to%20another%20terrain%20altogether.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20sections%20in%20the%20book%20deals%20with%20hypothetical%20situations%20such%20as%20the%20necessity%2C%20or%20not%2C%20of%20a%20bath%20following%20reprehensible%20acts%20such%20as%20paedophilia%2C%20bestiality%20and%20necrophilia.%20The%20question%20is%2C%20would%20anyone%20indulging%20in%20such%20reprehensible%20acts%20be%20bothered%20about%20the%20importance%2C%20or%20not%2C%20of%20taking%20a%20bath%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20any%20case%2C%20no%20sensible%20person%20would%20consider%20this%20advice%20as%20part%20of%20any%20guide%20of%20personal%20conduct%20or%20religion.%20And%20if%20someone%20indulging%20in%20acts%20beyond%20the%20pale%20were%20to%20seek%20validity%20from%20any%20religious%20source%20or%20text%2C%20that%20person%E2%80%99s%20search%20would%20be%20fruitless.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fundamental%20question%20then%20is%20whether%20the%20author%20of%20%3Cem%3EBahishti%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Zewar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20should%20have%20chosen%20to%20write%20hypothetically%20about%20such%20matters.%20But%20to%20accuse%20him%20of%20legitimising%20such%20acts%20would%20be%20stretching%20things%20too%20far.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20one%20can%20and%20should%20say%20is%20that%20if%20there%20was%20a%20reason%20why%20the%20author%20wrote%20about%20these%20matters%2C%20then%20a%20footnote%20was%20necessary%20to%20avoid%20the%20dangers%20of%20mis-reading.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIronically%2C%20there%20have%20also%20been%20attempts%20to%20tar%20with%20the%20same%20brush%20even%20those%20sections%20in%20which%20the%20author%20mentions%20women%E2%80%99s%20literacy%20or%20means%20to%20empower%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20can%20safely%20be%20said%20that%20every%20possible%20barb%20of%20criticism%20has%20already%20been%20aimed%20at%20%3Cem%3EBahishti%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Zewar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20that%20too%20long%20ago.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20nutshell%2C%20this%20early%2020%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century%20text%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20an%20attempt%20to%20educate%20women.%20However%2C%20it%20should%20have%20come%20with%20a%20cautionary%20statement%20that%20all%2010%20sections%20of%20it%20were%20not%20universally%20appropriate.%20Otherwise%2C%20it%20would%20appear%20dirty%2C%20as%20it%20did%20to%20a%20young%20Ismat%20Chughtai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EA%20text%20that%20is%20not%20a%20stranger%20to%20controversy%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20it%20is%20a%20first%20for%20Darul%20Uloom%20Deoband%20to%20come%20within%20the%20range%20of%20controversy%20that%20has%20always%20surrounded%20%3Cem%3EBahishti%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Zewar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20latter%20has%20been%20criticised%20frequently.%20At%20times%20so-called%20religious%20matters%20discussed%20in%20it%20have%20been%20called%20misleading%20in%20many%20quarters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20pervasive%20existence%20of%20caste%20among%20Muslims%20in%20India%2C%20several%20critics%20have%20described%20%3Cem%3EBahishti%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Zewar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EManusmriti%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eof%20Indian%20Muslims.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20question%20of%20caste%20arises%20in%20the%20book%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20subject%20of%20marriage%2C%20where%20the%20text%20openly%20speaks%20of%20the%20Sayyids%20being%20right%20on%20top%20of%20the%20hierarchical%20scale%20on%20account%20of%20birth%2C%20stating%20that%20a%20marriage%20between%20a%20so-called%20upper%20caste%20man%20and%20a%20so-called%20lower%20caste%20woman%20would%20be%20a%20mismatch.%20The%20author%20then%20goes%20on%20to%20determine%20the%20status%20of%20other%20castes%20as%20well.%20It%20can%20be%20said%20that%20the%20book%20displays%20an%20upper-caste%20mindset.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20conclusion%2C%20a%20few%20words%20about%20Maulana%20Ashraf%20Ali%20Thanawi%20(1863-1943)%2C%20the%20author%20of%20%3Cem%3EBahishti%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Zewar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20He%20was%20considered%20a%20prominent%20scholar%20of%20his%20time%2C%20and%20apart%20from%20being%20known%20for%20some%20significant%20articles%20of%20criticism%20in%20the%20context%20of%20literary%20works%2C%20he%20has%20authored%20several%20texts%20on%20issues%20of%20religion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20regards%20his%20political%20stance%2C%20he%20was%20a%20staunch%20supporter%20of%20the%20Muslim%20League.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20considered%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20and%20Gandhi%20to%20be%20enemies%20of%20Muslims.%20When%20support%20for%20the%20Congress%20grew%20in%20Darul%20Uloom%20and%20Deoband%20decided%20to%20openly%20support%20the%20Congress%2C%20Thanawi%20lost%20no%20time%20in%20resigning%20from%20the%20institution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20would%20right-wing%20activists%20hope%20to%20gain%20by%20spotlighting%20a%20contested%20text%20by%20such%20an%20author%20other%20than%20creating%20a%20climate%20of%20opinion%20against%20Muslims%3F%20If%20the%20complainants%20had%20the%20well-being%20of%20fellow%20Muslim%20citizens%20in%20mind%2C%20all%20they%20had%20to%20do%20was%20demonstrate%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20text%20validated%20caste%20hierarchy%20among%20Muslims%2C%20for%20that%20part%20of%20the%20book%20was%20not%20couched%20in%20hypothetical%20terms.%20But%20in%20doing%20that%2C%20the%20complainants%20would%20have%20been%20going%20against%20their%20own%20ideology.%C2%A0%20It%20is%20all%20well%20to%20mouth%20support%20for%20Pasmanda%20Muslims%2C%20but%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20doing%20something%20right%20by%20them%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20no-no.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20wonder%20the%20complainant%20fell%20back%20upon%20%3Cem%3EBahishti%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Zewar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20It%E2%80%99s%20always%20nice%20to%20have%20low-hanging%20fruit%20within%20arm%E2%80%99s%20distance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F255143%2Fdarul-uloom-deoband-bahishti-zewar-manushi-ncpcr%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20original%20by%20Chitra%20Padmanabhan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692434550000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19141006%2FDarul-Uloom-Bahishti-Zewar.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fbaheshti-zewar-darool-uloom-islamophobia%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20would%20right-wing%20activists%20hope%20to%20gain%20by%20spotlighting%20a%20contested%20text%20other%20than%20creating%20a%20climate%20of%20opinion%20against%20Muslims%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fbaheshti-zewar-darool-uloom-islamophobia%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20PM%20Modi's%20TB%20Deadline%20Looms%2C%20Govt%20Must%20Know%20That%20Not%20Counting%20Isn't%20an%20Option%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19133349%2F10146202616_81d4c004a4_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20food%20is%20India%E2%80%99s%20Achilles%20Heel%20in%20tuberculosis%20control%20has%20been%20reiterated%20by%20the%20brilliantly%20intuitive%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research-backed%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelancet.com%2Fjournals%2Flanglo%2Farticle%2FPIIS2214-109X(23)00324-8%2Ffulltext%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20study%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20how%20food%20baskets%20can%20prevent%20secondary%20infections%20in%20family%20members%20of%20TB%20patients.%20But%20for%20India%20the%20bigger%20challenge%20in%20TB%20has%20been%20keeping%20count%20%E2%80%93%20the%20patient%20needs%20to%20be%20identified%20and%20put%20on%20treatment%20first%20before%20measures%20are%20instituted%20to%20safeguard%20their%20families.%20Food%20baskets%2C%20the%20study%20also%20showed%2C%20can%20reduce%20TB%20mortality%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20a%20fraction%20of%20actual%20TB%20cases%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2FPolitics%2FmaQIfJzHsg2LenYO5k3OxI%2FIndia-a-major-contributor-to-underdiagnosis-of-tuberculosis.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20this%20despite%20the%202012%20notification%20making%20non%20reporting%20a%20punishable%20offence%20%E2%80%93%20and%20many%20more%20probably%20continue%20to%20evade%20the%20formal%20system%2C%20often%20seeking%20succour%20in%20quackery.%20India%E2%80%99s%20decision%20earlier%20this%20year%20to%20maintain%20its%20own%20count%20of%20TB%20making%20it%20the%20first%20country%20to%20move%20away%20from%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20numbers%20could%20add%20another%20level%20of%20complexity%2C%20potentially%20breeding%20complacency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20evocative%20though%20it%20is%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20food%20as%20a%20vaccine%20for%20tuberculosis%20is%20not%20a%20comforting%20one%20in%20a%20country%20that%20has%20the%20highest%20burden%20of%20the%20disease%20in%20the%20world%20and%20ranks%20107%20out%20of%20121%20countries%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.globalhungerindex.org%2Findia.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EGlobal%20Hunger%20Index%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20levels%20of%20hunger%20being%20termed%20%E2%80%9Cserious%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Union%20government%20has%20labelled%20the%20GHI%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fglobal-hunger-index-attempt-to-tarnish-indias-image-centre%2Farticle66015191.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etaint%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20India.%20Now%20one%20can%20only%20hope%20that%20with%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20promised%20deadline%20of%202025%20to%20eliminate%20TB%20looming%20large%2C%20the%20findings%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ELancet%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3Es%20study%20on%20the%20efficacy%20of%20food%20baskets%20as%20a%20means%20to%20reduce%20secondary%20TB%20infections%20among%20family%20members%20will%20find%20a%20place%20in%20the%20basket%20of%20government%20interventions%20against%20the%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20is%20further%20proof%20that%20undernutrition%20is%20one%20of%20the%20key%20drivers%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20TB%20epidemic.%20The%20infection%20is%20so%20common%20among%20Indians%20that%20a%20skin%20test%20widely%20used%20for%20detection%20of%20the%20bacterium%20is%20not%20the%20test%20of%20choice%20in%20India.%20That%20is%20because%20the%20test%20gives%20a%20positive%20result%20for%20exposure%20and%20in%20India%20it%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1808092%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eestimated%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%2040%25%20people%20carry%20the%20infection%20while%20only%2010%25%20develop%20the%20disease.%20The%20difference%20between%20a%20carrier%20and%20a%20patient%20is%20their%20immunity%20%E2%80%93%20linked%20to%20a%20large%20part%20to%20nutrition%20%E2%80%93%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETB%20diagnosis%20of%20course%20has%20made%20several%20strides%20in%20recent%20years%20to%20keep%20pace%20with%20the%20emerging%20challenge%20of%20drug%20resistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESystemic%20challenges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20systemic%20issues%20plague%20India%E2%80%99s%20TB%20war%20and%20some%20of%20those%20are%20hidden%20in%20the%20last%20few%20pages%20of%20the%20India%20TB%20report%202023%20released%20in%20March%20this%20year%20by%20PM%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20estimated%20that%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.path.org%2Fcase-studies%2Fprivate-sector-tb-india-ppia%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNearly%25252080%252520percent%252520of%252520people%2Cthe%252520number%252520of%252520TB%252520cases.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E80%25%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20TB%20patients%20seek%20treatment%20from%20the%20private%20sector.%20However%20data%20published%20in%20the%20government%20report%20show%20that%20only%2030%25%20of%20TB%20notifications%20happen%20from%20the%20private%20sector.%20This%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20disease%20was%20made%20notifiable%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fnews-archive%2Fweb%2Fcentre-to-make-tb-notifiable-disease%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E2012%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20subsequently%20not%20notifying%20it%20became%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Flifestyle%2Fhealth%2Fdoctors-and-chemists-can-be-jailed-if-they-dont-report-tb-5105218%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epunishable%20offence%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20TB%20patient%20that%20is%20not%20notified%20is%20one%20that%20misses%20out%20on%20the%20nutrition%20stipend%20they%20are%20eligible%20for%20and%20is%20also%20one%20that%20is%20out%20of%20the%20web%20of%20health%20workers%20who%20ensure%20patient%20adherence%20to%20the%20minimum%20six%20month%20course%20of%20anti%20tubercular%20drugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20challenges%20beyond%20what%20the%20TB%20report%20captures.%20A%20particularly%20daunting%20one%20remains%20access%20to%20healthcare%20services%20which%2C%20contrary%20to%20perception%2C%20is%20not%20just%20a%20function%20of%20availability.%20The%20organised%20healthcare%20system%20for%20reasons%20that%20have%20been%20dealt%20with%20at%20length%20in%20various%20academic%20papers%20intimidates%20and%20in-dignifies%20India%E2%80%99s%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20why%20their%20%E2%80%9Cdoctor%E2%80%9D%20of%20choice%20is%20often%20a%20quack%20%E2%80%93%20euphemistically%20referred%20to%20often%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinformal%E2%80%9D%20sector.%20Post%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20National%20Rural%20Health%20Mission%20and%20Ayushman%20Bharat%2C%20it%20is%20the%20Indian%20cities%20that%20are%20fertile%20hunting%20grounds%20for%20quacks%2C%20much%20more%20than%20rural%20India.%20The%20cities%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20crowded%20and%20unsanitary%20living%20conditions%20for%20migrant%20workers%2C%20are%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F27865238%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebreeding%20grounds%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20tuberculosis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%20for%20many%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20urban%20poor%20quacks%20remain%20the%20first%20ports%20of%20call%20and%20%E2%80%9Cfamily%20doctors%E2%80%9D%20in%20any%20health%20event%20%E2%80%93%20so%20much%20so%20that%20on%20occasions%20when%20they%20have%20reached%20the%20DOTS%20Centre%2C%20peer%20pressure%2C%20coupled%20with%20the%20unpalatable%20drug%20reactions%20make%20many%20drop%20out%20and%20seek%20remedy%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brookings.edu%2Farticles%2Fof-quacks-and-crooks-the-conundrum-of-informal-health-care-in-india%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Equackery%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Money%20is%20not%20always%20the%20motivation%20%E2%80%93%20quacks%20can%20and%20do%20charge%20a%20fairly%20high%20price%20for%20their%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKeeping%20count%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2022%2F04%2F16%2Fhealth%2Fglobal-covid-deaths-who-india.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esparred%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20WHO%20over%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20COVID19%20death%20count%20and%20neither%20side%20budged%20from%20their%20perspective%20positions.%20In%20the%20aftermath%20of%20that%20long%20and%20occasionally%20acrimonious%20exchange%2C%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fhealth%2Findia-challenges-who-global-modelling-estimates-for-tb-is-first-to-develop-own-model%2F1479384%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eunveiled%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20March%20this%20year%20a%20new%20modelling%20system%20to%20count%20TB%20cases%20%E2%80%94%20the%20first%20country%20in%20the%20world%20to%20do%20so.%20The%20model%20has%20dramatically%20spruced%20up%20India%E2%80%99s%20report%20card%2C%20with%20TB%20incidence%20down%20to%20196%20per%20100%2C000%20population%20instead%20of%20the%20210%20estimated%20by%20WHO%20and%20total%20TB%20deaths%20in%202021%20down%20from%20WHO%E2%80%99s%204.94%20lakh%20to%203.20%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TB%20mortality%20rate%20%E2%80%94%20according%20to%20the%20Indian%20model%20%E2%80%94%20stands%20at%2023%20per%201%2C00%2C000%20people%20against%20the%2035%20that%20WHO%20had%20estimated%20in%202022.%20WHO%20estimates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20disparity%20though%20is%20in%20the%20number%20of%20missing%20cases%20during%202020-2021%20when%20a%20slew%20of%20factors%20including%20lockdown%20and%20diversion%20of%20TB%20control%20manpower%20on%20pandemic%20duties%20caused.%20WHO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Findia-tops-world-in-unreported-tuberculosis-cases-1041839.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eestimates%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20India%20missed%20out%20on%20diagnosing%2041%20lakh%20cases.%20India%20estimates%20that%20it%20missed%20about%204%20lakh%20cases%20each%20in%202020%20and%202021.%20The%20total%20number%20of%20TB%20notifications%20in%202022%20stood%20at%2024.2%20lakh%20cases%20%E2%80%94%20the%20highest%20ever%20but%20only%20marginally%20above%20the%20count%20for%202019%2C%20the%20last%20pre-pandemic%20year%2C%20when%20it%20stood%20at%2023.9%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20change%20goalposts%20in%20a%20challenge%20as%20recalcitrant%20as%20TB%20immediately%20after%20the%20biggest%20disruption%20since%20the%20inception%20of%20the%20TB%20control%20programme%20could%20be%20catastrophic.%20To%20project%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cprogress%E2%80%9D%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20new%20domestic%20calculation%20vis%20%C3%A0%20vis%3Cbr%3E%5Cnthe%20earlier%20international%20one%20is%20like%20comparing%20apples%20and%20oranges.%20What%E2%80%99s%20more%2C%20it%20would%20perpetuate%20a%20sense%20of%20complacency%20and%20take%20away%20from%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20last%20few%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20may%20be%20spared%20the%20ignominy%20of%20being%20the%20country%20with%20the%20worst%20TB%20incidence%20but%20that%20sheen%20would%20come%20at%20a%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20India%20incorporates%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20ICMR%20backed%20study%20on%20food%20packets%20for%20contacts%20or%20not%2C%20the%20first%20step%20in%20the%20control%20of%20any%20disease%20and%20in%20its%20eventual%20elimination%20is%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20problem%20and%20not%20attempt%20to%20trivialise%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ci%3EAbantika%20Ghosh%20is%20a%20former%20journalist%20and%20author%20of%20%3C%2Fi%3EBillions%20Under%20Lockdown%3A%20The%20Inside%20Story%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Fight%20Against%20COVID-19.%3Ci%3E%20She%20is%20currently%20working%20with%20Chase%20India.%20She%20tweets%20%40abantika77.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692432684000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19133349%2F10146202616_81d4c004a4_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Ftuberculosis-india-count-who-narendra-modi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Not%20detecting%20TB%20cases%20means%20worse%20outcomes%20for%20the%20patient%2C%20more%20cases%20among%20first%20degree%20contacts%20and%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%20rising%20incidence%20of%20drug-resistant%20TB.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Ftuberculosis-india-count-who-narendra-modi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Can%20Rinku%20emulate%20Dhoni%20and%20Yuvraj's%20finishing%20skills%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692432643000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102853963%2Cimgsize-79096.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fcan-rinku-singh-emulate-ms-dhoni-and-yuvraj-singhs-finishing-skills-heres-what-this-former-india-cricketer-thinks%2Farticleshow%2F102853872.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Indian%20wicketkeeper-batsman%20holds%20the%20belief%20that%20young%20batting%20sensation%20Rinku%20Singh%20possesses%20the%20potential%20to%20emerge%20as%20an%20exceptional%20closer%2C%20akin%20to%20the%20legendary%20MS%20Dhoni%20and%20Yuvraj%20Singh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A116%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fcan-rinku-singh-emulate-ms-dhoni-and-yuvraj-singhs-finishing-skills-heres-what-this-former-india-cricketer-thinks%2Farticleshow%2F102853872.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bihar%20Caste%20Census%3A%20SC%20Refuses%20to%20Stay%20Release%20of%20Data%2C%20Says%20It%20Doesn't%20Violate%20Right%20to%20Privacy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F07202552%2FScreenshot-2022-02-07-at-8.25.47-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20refused%20to%20stay%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20census%20and%20dismissed%20the%20petitioners%E2%80%99%20reasoning%20that%20it%20violates%20a%20citizen%E2%80%99s%20fundamental%20right%20to%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20data%20collection%20exercise%20was%20already%20completed%20on%20August%206%2C%20the%20petitioners%20opposing%20the%20move%20sought%20an%20order%20from%20the%20top%20court%20to%20stay%20the%20release%20or%20uploading%20of%20the%20data%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20However%2C%20the%20court%20declined%20their%20plea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fbihar-caste-survey-no-supreme-court-stay-on-publication-of-data%2Farticle67209919.ece%5C%22%3E%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20observed%2C%20%E2%80%9CHow%20is%20the%20right%20to%20privacy%20affected%20when%20somebody%20is%20asked%20to%20give%20his%20caste%20or%20sub-caste%3F%20That%20individual%20data%20is%20not%20released%20to%20the%20public%E2%80%A6%20What%20is%20released%20is%20the%20cumulative%20figures.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20senior%20advocate%20C.S.%20Vaidyanathan%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20NGO%20Youth%20for%20Equality%2C%20said%20that%20people%20could%20not%20be%20%E2%80%9Ccompelled%20to%20reveal%20their%20caste%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%2C%20Justice%20Khanna%20responded%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CYour%20caste%20is%20known%20to%20your%20neighbours%E2%80%A6.%20Which%20of%20the%2017%20questions%20asked%20in%20the%20survey%20amounts%20to%20a%20violation%20of%20privacy%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVaidyanathan%20then%20argued%20that%20the%20only%20thing%20voluntary%20among%20the%20list%20of%20questions%20on%20caste%2C%20religion%2C%20and%20personal%20income%20was%20Aadhar%20information%20and%20nothing%20else.%20He%20sought%20to%20convey%20that%20disclosing%20one%E2%80%99s%20caste%20was%20made%20compulsory%20under%20the%20survey%2C%20adding%20it%20was%20not%20%E2%80%9Ctoday%E2%80%99s%20thinking%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Khanna%20denied%20that%20there%20was%20an%20element%20of%20compulsion.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20penalty%20involved%20if%20a%20person%20chooses%20not%20to%20fill%20this%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20in%20support%20of%20the%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%20also%20questioned%20that%20the%20survey%20had%20been%20undertaken%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20mere%20executive%20order%2C%20passed%20on%20June%206%20last%20year%2C%20but%20not%20with%20statutory%20backing.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20a%20survey%20such%20as%20this%20%E2%80%93%20which%20impinged%20on%20a%20fundamental%20right%20of%20privacy%20%E2%80%93%20should%20have%20a%20statutory%20basis%20and%20an%20administrative%20order%20from%20the%20political%20executive%20would%20not%20suffice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20fundamental%20right%20cannot%20be%20infringed%20upon%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20an%20administrative%20order%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBihar%20government%E2%80%99s%20counsel%2C%20Shyam%20Divan%2C%20however%2C%20dismissed%20the%20arguments%20of%20the%20petitioners%2C%20calling%20them%20%E2%80%9Ccompletely%20motivated%E2%80%9D.%20He%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20survey%20was%20already%20concluded%2C%20on%20August%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20social%20survey.%20The%20information%20got%20from%20the%20exercise%20would%20be%20analysed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Divan%20said.%20He%20also%20went%20on%20to%20add%20that%20information%20collected%20from%20the%20survey%20would%20help%20the%20Bihar%20government%20to%20better%20its%20delivery%20of%20welfare%20programmes.%20He%20assured%20that%20individual%20data%20would%20be%20protected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20rejected%20the%20plea%20of%20another%20petitioner%20who%20also%20sought%20a%20stay%20on%20the%20uploading%2Fdisclosing%20data%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20not%20stay%20anything%20till%20we%20are%C2%A0%3Ci%3Eprima%20facie%3C%2Fi%3E%20convinced%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20that%E2%80%A6%20The%20State%20has%20already%20a%20High%20Court%20judgment%20in%20its%20favour.%20The%20exercise%20is%20complete.%20The%20data%20will%20be%20available%20in%20public%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Khanna%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20dismissed%20the%20argument%20of%20the%20petitioners%20that%20the%20Bihar%20government%20is%20not%20empowered%20to%20carry%20out%20such%20a%20survey%2C%20for%20the%20authority%20to%20conduct%20a%20census%20rests%20only%20with%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nitish%20Kumar%20government%20launched%20a%20caste%20census%20in%20Bihar%20in%20January%20this%20year%2C%20stating%20that%20detailed%20information%20on%20the%20socio-economic%20conditions%20of%20the%20people%20in%20the%20state%20would%20help%20create%20better%20government%20policy%20to%20aid%20disadvantaged%20groups.%20The%20entire%20exercise%20was%20supposed%20to%20have%20been%20completed%20by%20May.%20However%2C%20the%20legal%20challenges%20meant%20the%20government%20was%20unable%20to%20complete%20the%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caste%20census%20has%20become%20a%20major%20political%20concern%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20with%20opposition%20parties%20exerting%20pressure%20on%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20do%20the%20exercise%20on%20a%20national%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692430388000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F07202552%2FScreenshot-2022-02-07-at-8.25.47-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbihar-caste-census-sc-refuses-to-stay-release-of-data-says-it-doesnt-violate-right-to-privacy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20data%20collection%20exercise%20was%20already%20completed%20on%20August%206%2C%2