%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fmurders-of-govind-pansarenarendra-dabholkar-mm-kalburgi-gauri-lankesh-interconnected-dabholkars-daughter-tells-supreme-court-235534%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20bench%20told%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20Aishwarya%20Bhati%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20CBI%2C%20that%20the%20CBI%20could%20examine%20the%20issue%20of%20a%20larger%20conspiracy%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20additional%20documents%20filed%20by%20Dabholkar%E2%80%99s%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Advocate%20Anand%20Grover%2C%20appearing%20for%20her%2C%20said%20that%20the%20CBI%20investigation%20was%20not%20completed%20when%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%20passed%20its%20order.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20perfunctory%20evidence%20indicated%20that%20the%20murders%20of%20Govind%20Pansare%2C%20Dr.%20Narendra%20Dabholkar%2C%20Professor%20MM%20Kalburgi%2C%20and%20Gauri%20Lankesh%20are%20interconnected%2C%E2%80%9D%20Grover%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Justice%20Dhulia%20asked%20what%20was%20wrong%20with%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20observation%20that%20it%20will%20not%20monitor%20the%20case%20in%20which%20trial%20was%20ongoing%20and%20several%20witnesses%20had%20been%20examined%2C%20Grover%20said%20that%20the%20absconding%20accused%20had%20not%20been%20arrested%20yet%20%E2%80%93%20despite%20which%20a%20trial%20was%20afoot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20%E2%80%9Clarger%20conspiracy%E2%80%9D%20angle%2C%20the%20ASG%20said%20that%20among%20the%20five%20accused%20sufficient%20evidence%20is%20not%20there%20against%20three%2C%20and%20the%20other%20two%20are%20not%20connected.%20Another%20five%20accused%20are%20undergoing%20trial%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20asked%20for%20clarity%20from%20the%20CBI%20on%20whether%20the%20accused%20who%20are%20on%20trial%20have%20no%20common%20thread%20between%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20a%20special%20Pune%20court%20framed%20charges%20against%20Virendra%20Sinh%20Tawde%2C%20who%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20alleged%20mastermind%20of%20Dabholkar%E2%80%99s%20murder%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20charged%20him%20and%20three%20others%20were%20charged%20with%20murder%2C%20conspiracy%20and%20terror-related%20offences%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20Prevention%20Act.%20The%20fifth%20accused%2C%20advocate%20Sanjeev%20Punalekar%20was%20charged%20with%20destruction%20of%20evidence%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692428779000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F17134928%2FSupreme_Court_of_India_01-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-asks-cbi-to-look-into-larger-conspiracy-in-killings-of-dabholkar-pansare-kalburgi-lankesh%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20division%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20of%20Justices%20Sanjay%20Kishan%20Kaul%20and%20Sudhanshu%20Dhulia%2C%20was%20hearing%20a%20plea%20filed%20by%20Narendra%20Dabholkar's%20daughter%2C%20challenging%20the%20Bombay%20HC's%20refusal%20to%20continue%20monitoring%20his%20murder%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-asks-cbi-to-look-into-larger-conspiracy-in-killings-of-dabholkar-pansare-kalburgi-lankesh%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22West%20Ham%20midfielder%20withdrawn%20from%20Brazil%20squad%20amid%20betting%20investigation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692427380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F08%2F768x432%2Fskynews-west-ham-lucas-paqueta_6255409.jpg%3F20230819075306%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fwest-ham-midfielder-lucas-paqueta-withdrawn-from-brazil-squad-for-world-cup-qualifiers-amid-betting-investigation-12942786%22%2C%22su