20Rajeev%20Gowda%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttending%20participants%20had%20travelled%20from%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20according%20to%20the%20event%E2%80%99s%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20placed%20at%20the%20front%20and%20centre%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20G20%20is%20an%20%E2%80%9Cinformal%20elite%20club%E2%80%9D%20of%20traditional%20and%20selected%20powers%20whose%20decisions%20impact%20the%20policies%20and%20financial%20architecture%20of%20the%20whole%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20highlighted%20India%E2%80%99s%20enormous%20%E2%80%9CRs%2051%20crore%E2%80%9D%20outdoor%20advertising%20budget%20as%20host.%20In%20the%20process%20of%20beautifying%20cities%2C%20the%20speakers%20highlighted%20how%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20poor%20and%20their%20homes%20have%20not%20just%20been%20hidden%2C%20they%20have%20been%20evicted%20and%20their%20homes%20bulldozed%20in%20the%20cities%20where%20G20%20meetings%20took%20place.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fg20-cities-forced-evictions-beautification%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20how%20a%20recent%20study%20collating%20testimonies%20of%20those%20affected%20by%20forced%20evictions%20purportedly%20necessitated%20by%20India%20hosting%20the%20G20%20summit%20has%20unveiled%20a%20picture%20of%20particular%20administrative%20apathy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20people%20affected%20by%20the%20evictions%20at%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Bela%20Estate%20%E2%80%93%20Shakeel%20who%20works%20with%20the%20Basti%20Suraksha%20Manch%20and%20Rekha%20%E2%80%93%20spoke%20on%20their%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three-day%20programme%20will%20include%20nine%20workshops%20on%20global%20finance%2C%20banking%2C%20the%20right%20to%20information%2C%20data%20and%20digital%20surveillance%2C%20urban%20life%20and%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20economists%20Arun%20Kumar%20and%20Jayati%20Ghosh%20highlighted%20how%20the%20G20%20was%20moving%20away%20from%20%E2%80%9Cpeople-centric%E2%80%9D%20decisions%2C%20activists%20Medha%20Patkar%20and%20Teesta%20Setalvad%20questioned%20whose%20interests%20the%20G20%20was%20serving%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Manoj%20Jha%20said%20that%20the%20struggle%20to%20fight%20fascism%20is%20the%20combined%20fight%20from%20the%20roads%20to%20the%20parliament.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarsh%20Mander%20noted%20that%20%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20government%20does%20not%20change%20in%202024%2C%20the%20story%20of%20Manipur%20will%20be%20all%20of%20our%20stories.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20press%20release%20notes%20that%20more%20than%2070%20organisations%2C%20unions%20and%20peoples%E2%80%99%20groups%20including%20National%20Alliance%20of%20People%E2%80%99s%20Movements%2C%20Focus%20on%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20All%20India%20Union%20of%20Forest%20Working%20People%2C%20Narmada%20Bachao%20Andolan%2C%20Environment%20Support%20Group%20(ESG)%2C%20Peoples%20Resource%20Centre%2C%20People%20First%2C%20Alternative%20Law%20Forum%2C%20and%20others%20participated%20in%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692424091000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19105302%2Fa51bfc9b-877e-4f93-83b4-47bcc4ab75fb.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwe20-g20-new-delhi-event-teesta-setalvad-manoj-jha%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20event%20placed%20at%20the%20front%20and%20centre%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20G20%20is%20an%20'informal%20elite%20club'%20of%20traditional%20and%20selected%20powers%20whose%20decisions%20impact%20the%20policies%20and%20financial%20architecture%20of%20the%20whole%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwe20-g20-new-del