0released%20portions%20of%20his%20excrement%20along%20the%20passageway.%20Later%20in%20the%20day%2C%20a%20collection%20of%2010%20neighbourhood%20aunties%20stood%20outside%20his%20home%20complaining%20to%20his%20mother%20about%20what%20he%20did.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20hilariously%20denying%20his%20son%E2%80%99s%20involvement%20in%20the%20crime%2C%20Navin%E2%80%99s%20mother%20tells%20him%20something%20that%20he%20would%20hear%20again%20years%20later%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CApne%20mein%20chalta%20hai%2C%20bahar%20jaake%20mat%20karna%3C%2Fem%3E%20(do%20whatever%20you%20want%20within%20the%20confines%20of%20your%20private%20space%2C%20just%20don%E2%80%99t%20do%20it%20outside)%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYears%20later%2C%20when%20he%20finally%20found%20the%20courage%20to%20come%20out%20and%20introduce%20his%20partner%20to%20his%20mother%20at%2027%2C%20she%20didn%E2%80%99t%20reject%20his%20queer%20identity%2C%20but%20did%20say%20one%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CApne%20mein%20chalta%20hai%2C%20bahar%20jaake%20mat%20karna%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFast%20forward%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%20and%20it%20was%20Pride%20Month%20in%20Mumbai.%20Navin%20and%20his%20partner%20were%20photographed%20kissing%20each%20other%20on%20the%20front%20page%20of%20%3Cem%3EBombay%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20a%20cousin%20he%20dislikes%2C%20a%20screenshot%20of%20that%20photo%20was%20shared%20on%20the%20family%20WhatsApp%20group.%20Furious%20at%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20extended%20family%20finding%20out%20that%20her%20son%20is%20gay%2C%20Navin%E2%80%99s%20mother%20once%20again%20repeated%20that%20maxim%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20kicked%20him%20out%20of%20the%20house.%20Despite%20the%20initial%20pain%2C%20there%20was%20also%20a%20sense%20of%20relief%20for%20Navin.%20He%20and%20his%20partner%20ended%20up%20finding%20an%20apartment%20and%20started%20living%20together.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%