.%20My%20parents%20were%20unsure%20of%20this%20potential%20that%20I%20saw%20in%20the%20house%20as%20Ratnari%20is%20not%20a%20touristy%20place%2C%20to%20begin%20with%2C%20but%20more%20of%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298965%2Fdelhi-professiors-turn-traditional-houses-into-homestays-boost-sustainable-tourism-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoff-beat%20location%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20after%20much%20debate%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20ended%20up%20persuading%20them%20to%20let%20me%20experiment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20904px)%20100vw%2C%20904px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG-20230811-WA0020-1691756131.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22904%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chickens%2C%20ducks%20and%20more%20can%20be%20found%20on%20the%20property%20along%20with%20a%20kitchen%20garden%20that%20meets%20all%20the%20produce%20needs%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG-20230811-WA0020-1691756131.jpg%20904w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG-20230811-WA0020-1691756131-212x300.jpg%20212w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG-20230811-WA0020-1691756131-500x708.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG-20230811-WA0020-1691756131-768x1087.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG-20230811-WA0020-1691756131-150x212.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327065%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChickens%2C%20ducks%20and%20more%20can%20be%20found%20on%20the%20property%20along%20with%20a%20kitchen%20garden%20that%20meets%20all%20the%20produce%20needs%2C%20Pictu